                    <span>This book lays out all the wonderful and vulnerable properties and characteristics of natural stone in a home.  Flooring, countertops, tiles - and maintenance...... it's all in here.  The one place you really should look if you're considering these gorgeous organic looks for your home.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">ALL you need to Know</div>
